Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveFast rising Nigerian social media influencer, Opeyemi Kareem has been confirmed dead after he was reportedly crushed by a trailer on Saturday, April 9.
The news has since circulated amongst his friends, colleagues and fans and most of them took to his Instagram page which has 65,000 followers to express their shock as well wish the news wasn’t true.
Most of the commenters on his page were overwhelmed to see the sad news, as they attested to chatting with the deceased on WhatsApp App just a few minutes before the ugly incident took place in Lagos.
Opeyemi Kareem’s death is coming shortly after the death of gospel singer Osinachi, who died on Friday, April 8.





